Description: Provides methods for fuzzy unsupervised and
    semi-supervised clustering, including fuzzy, possibilistic,
    and hybrid models. The package introduces a generalized
    estimation framework that enables modular extensions of
    prototype-based fuzzy clustering algorithms.
